properties.areaDesc: Coastal Waters From Cape Flattery To James Island 10 To 60 Nm; Waters From James Island To Point Grenville 10 To 60 Nm; Coastal Waters From Point Grenville To Cape Shoalwater 10 To 60 Nm
properties.headline: Storm Warning issued January 15 at 3:05AM PST until January 15 at 7:00PM PST by NWS Seattle WA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southeast winds rising to 35 to 50 kt and seas building
to 18 to 23 feet at 12 seconds.

* WHERE...Coastal Waters From Cape Flattery To James Island 10
To 60 Nm, Coastal Waters From James Island To Point Grenville
10 To 60 Nm and Coastal Waters From Point Grenville To Cape
Shoalwater 10 To 60 Nm.

* WHEN...Until 7 PM PST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Very strong winds will cause hazardous seas which
could capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should remain in port, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: STORM WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 PM PST THIS EVENING
